  "description": "Pi constant at mid-depth. Slow LFO1 at 0.12 Hz sweeps convergent depth — because Pi's convergents are derived from a normal number, the shimmer pattern never exactly repeats. High resonator adds a chiming tail. The digits of pi as a spectral event horizon.",
